{"tid":1340692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家記住 光復元朗唔係還拖 而係延續時代革命","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:16:43.000Z","uid":198822,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0205f5d7fde96346598a63f3ca72dfddf0a9e3","tid":1340692,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"暴力要聲討。<br />\n大家見到市民同記者畀班圍村狗打，嬲係好正常。<br />\n但係政府都估到，所以幕後嘅人先會搵呢班垃圾出嚟做替死鬼，轉移民憤。<br />\n如果有光復元朗，我諗<span style=\"color: gold;\">個焦點係清洗呢個腐敗嘅制度。</span><br />\n<br />\n由黑社會、賊過興兵嘅黑警以至係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幕後蓄意挑動民憤，蠱惑人心嘅港共同中共；</span></span><br />\n呢啲畜生通通都要清算。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span></span></strong>已經開始咗，目標已經唔再係聲討暴力咁簡單。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fVefoO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fVefoO.png&h=157578a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c63ba3d9718c2e90a7d51f5004cc53c4d6d264","tid":1340692,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016fa29dce848c8c73ff3029f783e106291ad300","tid":1340692,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cb44cc182f5efc3f9fd565f9b071c2c3392c0384","tid":1340692,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd4f348131c9a97aacd1bdc8ec336b87451b7efc","tid":1340692,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c55d294e16b580b3e13c773e39307cebafd9088","tid":1340692,"uid":173849,"like":0,